<p>
<lb n="1"/><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> maitre gotre pavitre mahimavati haḷebīḍa
<lb n="2" break="no"/><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> ballāḷapṛthvīpāleṁdrasyānvavāye suma
<lb n="3" break="no"/>tiravataran viṭhṭhalakṣoṇipālaḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> ni <unclear>śaṁ</unclear> 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>kaṁ kuṁkaṇorvīṣvaghamuci mucukundāśrame rā
<lb n="5"/>jyamuccaiḥ sthalyāṁ prābhānavalyāṁmaḷabhata
<lb n="6"/>khiḷanādurgamākramya samyak <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> tadvaṁśa
<lb n="7" break="no"/>mauktikamaṇeḥ śritakāmadhenoḥ kānhoji
<lb n="8" break="no"/>nāma vahataḥ kṣitibharturaṁbā <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> ratnābhidhā vyaraca
<lb n="9" break="no"/>dāśritarājamauḷiḥ jñāneśvarāryagurubhaktisu
<lb n="10" break="no"/>sādhamuktiḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 2 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśālivāhanaśakābhidha
<lb n="11" break="no"/>vatsarāṇāṁ yāteṣu ṣoḍaśaśateṣu gataḥ parastāt <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="12"/>Aṣṭādaśasvapi ca nirgaḷiteṣu varṣeṣvekonaviṁ
<lb n="13"/>śa Iti yaṁ vidurīśvarābdam <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 3 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> tasmin Īśvara<unclear>va</unclear>tsa
<lb n="14" break="no"/>re himaṛtau pauṣe ca māse tithau paṁcamyāṁ budhavāsa
<lb n="15" break="no"/><unclear>re</unclear> śatabhiṣa<unclear>jyṛ</unclear>kṣe ca pakṣe site <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> ratnākhyā dhavalā
<lb n="16" break="no"/>calasya nikaṭe sā śaivagaṁgātaṭe kānhojīkṣiti
<lb n="17" break="no"/>pālakasya jananī kailāsamāsādayat <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 4 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ārā
<lb n="18" break="no"/>maṁ dhavalagirerupatyakāyāṁ Adhvanyaśramaharamaṁ
<lb n="19" break="no"/>ḍapābhirāmaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> mārtaṁḍānvayatilakotha mātṛbhaktyā
<lb n="20"/>kānhojikṣitipatirātanonma<unclear>no</unclear>jñaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 5 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ātre
<lb n="21" break="no"/>yagotrajanuṣā viduṣāṁ ma<unclear>te</unclear>na śrīvekaṭāryamakhi
<lb n="22" break="no"/>nā raghunāthasūreḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> putreṇa śeṣagirināthapadābja
<lb n="23" break="no"/>bhājā ślokā Ime viracitāḥ suciraṁ jayaṁtu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 6 <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

